attributes.title: ( ͠° ͟ʖ ͡°)
attributes.review:
When i got this app i was very happy to support the best president ever, first of all it took a whole month to download I thought it was my phone but I was wrong terribly wrong, when if finally did download everything on my phone glitched apps opened and closed and made my apps larger and smaller horrible I just bought this phone it could’ve been me so it was this app and I know it. After I got it fixed I signed up and it asked me for my phone number I was not going to give my phone number to a virus! But I gave my email. And after that I got so many spam emails and Eventually it got my phone number anyway! Then one day I went out and I see a chubby Cheeto in the distance he started to increase speed and then suddenly I black out and I am now in the trump tower. I was scared and worrying then suddenly someone takes of my blindfold it was the chubby Cheeto he tried to make me vote for him for president but as a underaged person I tried to tell him I couldn’t then suddenly he falls on me! I kick him off and I see the one in only Barron Trump with a tranquilizer gun in hand he stunned his own father and untied me he told me to run, and to run fast and don’t turn back he said we‘ll meet again one day. As I run back to my house FBI agents try to get me back to the Trump tower as I try to escape all of them I start to lose hope and suddenly I hear gunshots all around it was the ghost George Floyd he screams “run, run young one I can’t see another black soul die again run!”
Now I’m running and make it back home I take a nap and reevaluate what just happened. Worst app ever if I didn’t download this app this wouldn’t of happened 0 stars if I could rate it 0.( ͠° ͟ʖ ͡°)
